OL,6,GThis evening's planned 30-minute
OL,7,Gedition of Sportsday ended after
OL,8,Gfifteen minutes due to technical
OL,9,Gproblems.
OL,11,FEagle-eyed viewers may have noticed a
OL,12,Flack of BBC Sport on-screen graphics
OL,13,F(though the standard BBC News flipper
OL,14,Fwas present).
OL,16,FBut things went more noticeably awry
OL,17,Fafter a two-way with Hywel Griffith in
OL,18,FDoha, when presenter Hugh Ferris was
OL,19,Fleft reading one story after another to
OL,20,Fcamera.
OL,3,CSportsday cut short due to technical
OL,4,Cproblems
