OL,6,FWhen a video report failed to
OL,7,Fmaterialise, Hugh apologised: "You can
OL,8,Ftell we've been having some problems
OL,9,Fwith the pictures here at Sportsday at
OL,10,Fthe moment.
OL,12,F"So I'll just continue to tell you some
OL,13,Fof the other sports news that we've had
OL,14,Ftoday at the BBC Sports Centre."
OL,16,FEventually, the programme team through
OL,17,Fin the towel.
OL,3,CSportsday cut short due to technical
OL,4,Cproblems
