OL,6,FHugh told viewers: "That in the trade
OL,7,Fis called a bit of vamping. And I will
OL,8,Fend it now to put us all out of our
OL,9,Fmisery. But thank you very much indeed.
OL,11,F"All sorts of problems here with all of
OL,12,Four pictures. So that you don't have to
OL,13,Fput up with me any more, let's hand you
OL,14,Fto Matt Taylor who has got the
OL,15,Fweather."
OL,17,FAnd so at 7.45pm we had a pre-recoded
OL,18,Fweather bulletin from Matt Taylor. That
OL,19,Fwas followed by an unscheduled repeat
OL,20,Fof yesterday's edition of Newswatch.
